  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">An online bookstore sells novels and magazines. Each novel sells for $4, and each magazine sells for $1. If Sadie purchased a total of 11&nbsp;novels and magazines that have a combined selling price of $20, how many novels did she purchase?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p>2</p>\n"
